      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·清廟之什·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">維天之命.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>維天之命，於穆不已。
於乎不顯，文王之德之純。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The ordinances of Heaven,—
How
deep are they and unintermitting!
And oh! how illustrious
Was the singleness of the virtue of king Wăn!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
