      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·清廟之什·002.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">維天之命.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>假以溢我，我其收之。
駿惠我文王，曾孫篤之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How does he (now) show his kindness?
We will receive it,
Striving to be in accord with him, our ​king Wăn;
And may his remotest descendant be abundantly the same!</seg>
      </tuv>
